Panel C-SenMayo Enrichment Scores: PT-BPD vs Developmental Reference Groups

SenMayo enrichment scores were calculated using Gene Set Enrichment Analysis (GSEA) to assess senescence-associated transcriptional programs in PT-BPD (alveolar deficiency).

Workflow:

Gene expression signatures were obtained from the integrated pediatric lung snRNA-seq dataset.
SenMayo gene signatures were analyzed using GSEA.
Normalized enrichment scores (NES) were calculated for each cell population.
PT-BPD samples were compared with developmental reference groups.
Results were visualized using GraphPad Prism.

Software:

GSEA (Broad Institute)
GraphPad Prism
